snippet.title: Run From Mummies - Official Announcement Trailer | Future Games Show 2024
snippet.description:
Check out the gameplay trailer for Run From Mummies, a 4-player co-op action game packed full of combat and secrets to uncover from Ancient Egypt.

Run From Mummies is coming to PlayStation and PC in Fall 2024.
